      "content": "breathing exercises dont really help when i actually feel the tightness. my friend said that if i just take more albuterol it'll work just fine and i won't need to wait weeks for an appointment. if i take 4 puffs every time i feel winded instead of 2, is that really gonna hurt me? it's just a rescue inhaler anyway right?",
